{"data": [{"id": "4742622", "title": "Why Is The Jobs Report So Important?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businesspeople carrying boxes around on painted lanes on asphalt\" data-id=\"912016096\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The bull run into year-end took a break yesterday for no reason other than investors must be gasping for air at the elevated altitude of 6,000 for the S&amp;P 500 and 45,000 for the Dow Jones Industrial Average. Except</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912016096/image_912016096.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742622-why-is-the-jobs-report-so-important", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 17:50:38"}, {"id": "4742637", "title": "VanEck Crypto Monthly Recap For November 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1419599523/image_1419599523.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Making Money in the Meta verse\" data-id=\"1419599523\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">We Are</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>November sparked a crypto revival with Trump\u2019s pro-crypto cabinet picks. Ethereum revealed faster block times and quantum-resistant upgrades, while Solana set revenue records amid memecoin mania.</em></p> <p><em>Please note that VanEck may have a position(s) in the digital asset(s) described</em></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742637-vaneck-crypto-monthly-recap-for-november-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 17:46:00"}, {"id": "4742615", "title": "Intel: The Problems Gelsinger Leaves Behind", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1670843479/image_1670843479.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Intel headquarters in Santa Clara, California, USA\" data-id=\"1670843479\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1670843479/image_1670843479.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1670843479/image_1670843479.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1670843479/image_1670843479.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1670843479/image_1670843479.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1670843479/image_1670843479.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1670843479/image_1670843479.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1670843479/image_1670843479.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1670843479/image_1670843479.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The sudden departure of Intel (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC</a></span>) CEO Pat Gelsinger this week laid bare the myriad problems that Intel faces. Of these, the most pressing are the lagging efforts to regain semiconductor process leadership as well as contending with Nvidia\u2019s (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1670843479/image_1670843479.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742615-intel-problems-gelsinger-leaves-behind", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 17:35:26"}, {"id": "4742613", "title": "Why CrowdStrike Still Has More Room To Run", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/147456329/image_147456329.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"IT Engineer in Action Configuring Servers\" data-id=\"147456329\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/147456329/image_147456329.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/147456329/image_147456329.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/147456329/image_147456329.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/147456329/image_147456329.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/147456329/image_147456329.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/147456329/image_147456329.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/147456329/image_147456329.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/147456329/image_147456329.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">baranozdemir</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>CrowdStrike (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CRWD\" title=\"CrowdStrike Holdings, Inc.\">CRWD</a></span>) has exceeded expectations, surpassing our optimistic <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4729612-whats-fuelling-crowdstrike-crwd-market-rebound\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4729612-whats-fuelling-crowdstrike-crwd-market-rebound\" target=\"_blank\">price target of $363</a> and delivering over <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4707554-crowdstrike-stock-path-to-recovery\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4707554-crowdstrike-stock-path-to-recovery\" target=\"_blank\">41% gains</a> since our post-outage coverage in July. The company continues to solidify its position as a leader in the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/147456329/image_147456329.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742613-why-crowdstrike-still-has-more-room-to-run", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 17:30:19"}, {"id": "4742627", "title": "November Jobs Report: A Return To Normalcy Following Flat October", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business colleagues meeting in modern conference room\" data-id=\"2155192216\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">MoMo Productions</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The November jobs report reflected a return to normalcy following an <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4732009-october-jobs-report-hurricanes-and-strike-activity-spook-payroll-growth\">October readout</a> that showed job gains as essentially flat from the month prior. As one of the final major datapoints ahead of the upcoming Federal Open Market Committee (\"FOMC\") meeting, the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2155192216/image_2155192216.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742627-november-jobs-report-a-return-to-normalcy-following-flat-october", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 17:20:42"}, {"id": "4742446", "title": "ICL Group: Looking Beyond US Borders And Finding Value In Israel", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"USA &amp; Israeli Flags\" data-id=\"184315804\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">DeniseBush/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I am stepping out briefly from my ardent risk-manager mantra. I usually cover dividend stocks, ETFs and macro strategy. And when I do write about more exciting market areas, it is usually along the lines of using a Magnificent 7 stock's volatility to earn</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184315804/image_184315804.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742446-icl-group-looking-beyond-us-borders-finding-value-in-israel", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 17:00:00"}, {"id": "4742606", "title": "Procore: Future Remains Bright", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"House project in virtual reality\" data-id=\"1351472483\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351472483/image_1351472483.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw